goal:
完全重寫 CameraView，做到跟 Apple 原生相機一樣的全螢幕佈局。

## 核心原則

**相機預覽必須是整個螢幕的背景**，所有控制元件浮在上面。不能有任何 padding、margin、frame 限制。

## 先讀取 docs/design-spec.md 了解設計規範

## CameraPreviewView.swift — 確保用 layerClass 方式

```swift
class PreviewUIView: UIView {
    override class var layerClass: AnyClass {
        AVCaptureVideoPreviewLayer.self
    }
    var previewLayer: AVCaptureVideoPreviewLayer {
        layer as! AVCaptureVideoPreviewLayer
    }
}

struct CameraPreviewView: UIViewRepresentable {
    let session: AVCaptureSession
    func makeUIView(context: Context) -> PreviewUIView {
        let view = PreviewUIView()
        view.previewLayer.session = session
        view.previewLayer.videoGravity = .resizeAspectFill
        view.backgroundColor = .black
        return view
    }
    func updateUIView(_ uiView: PreviewUIView, context: Context) {}
}
```

## CameraView.swift — 全螢幕 ZStack

```swift
var body: some View {
    ZStack {
        // 第 1 層：全黑背景（防閃爍）
        Color.black.ignoresSafeArea()

        // 第 2 層：相機預覽（滿版）
        #if targetEnvironment(simulator)
        simulatorPlaceholder
        #else
        CameraPreviewView(session: viewModel.captureSession)
        #endif

        // 第 3 層：所有控制元件
        VStack(spacing: 0) {
            // 頂部工具列
            HStack {
                flashButton
                Spacer()
                gridButton
                Spacer()
                timerButton
            }
            .padding(.horizontal, 20)
            .padding(.top, 8)
            .background(
                LinearGradient(colors: [.black.opacity(0.5), .clear],
                               startPoint: .top, endPoint: .bottom)
                .ignoresSafeArea(edges: .top)
            )

            Spacer()

            // 底部控制區
            VStack(spacing: 16) {
                // 濾鏡橫條
                filterStripView

                // 拍照 / 前後鏡頭 / 最近照片
                HStack(spacing: 40) {
                    lastPhotoThumbnail
                        .frame(width: 48, height: 48)
                    captureButton
                        .frame(width: 72, height: 72)
                    switchCameraButton
                        .frame(width: 48, height: 48)
                }

                // Photo / Video 切換
                modeSelector
            }
            .padding(.bottom, 20)
            .background(
                LinearGradient(colors: [.clear, .black.opacity(0.6)],
                               startPoint: .top, endPoint: .bottom)
                .ignoresSafeArea(edges: .bottom)
            )
        }
    }
    .ignoresSafeArea()
    .statusBarHidden(true)
}
```

**關鍵**：
- 整個 ZStack 用 `.ignoresSafeArea()`
- CameraPreviewView 不需要額外的 ignoresSafeArea（它在 ZStack 裡自然全螢幕）
- 頂部工具列用向下漸層黑色背景
- 底部控制區用向上漸層黑色背景
- 中間是純透明的，完全看到相機預覽

## simulatorPlaceholder — 也要全螢幕

```swift
private var simulatorPlaceholder: some View {
    ZStack {
        // 模擬一個相機取景器的感覺
        Color(white: 0.05)
        VStack(spacing: 24) {
            Image(systemName: "camera.viewfinder")
                .font(.system(size: 80, weight: .ultraLight))
                .foregroundStyle(.white.opacity(0.3))
            Text("Camera Preview")
                .font(.system(size: 16, weight: .medium))
                .foregroundStyle(.white.opacity(0.4))
        }
    }
}
```

